<Link id="l00185" /><CodeLine lineNumber="185"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// cross-CU DIE sharing is used in LTO and removes type redundancy at that</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00186" /><CodeLine lineNumber="186"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// level already) but may be implementable for some value in projects</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00187" /><CodeLine lineNumber="187"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// building multiple independent libraries with LTO and then linking those</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00188" /><CodeLine lineNumber="188"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// together.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01718" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1718"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// We can&#39;t use DT-&gt;getAlignInBits() here: AlignInBits for member type</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01719" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1719"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// is non-zero if and only if alignment was forced (e.g. &#95;Alignas()),</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01720" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1720"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// which can&#39;t be done with bitfields. Thus we use FieldSize here.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01721" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1721"><Highlight kind="normal">      uint32&#95;t AlignInBits = FieldSize;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01722" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1722"><Highlight kind="normal">      uint32&#95;t AlignMask = ~(AlignInBits - 1);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01723" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1723"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// The bits from the start of the storage unit to the start of the field.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01724" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1724"><Highlight kind="normal">      uint64&#95;t StartBitOffset = <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a05f5b9a11bdcc5feba62899f95dcf878a3134224cba2545bc57954d3b072aebb4">Offset</a> - (<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a05f5b9a11bdcc5feba62899f95dcf878a3134224cba2545bc57954d3b072aebb4">Offset</a> &amp; AlignMask);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01725" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1725"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// The byte offset of the field&#39;s aligned storage unit inside the struct.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01726" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1726"><Highlight kind="normal">      OffsetInBytes = (<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a05f5b9a11bdcc5feba62899f95dcf878a3134224cba2545bc57954d3b072aebb4">Offset</a> - StartBitOffset) / 8;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01727" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1727"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01728" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1728"><Highlight kind="normal">      </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordflow">if</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfunit-2/#a6688320f2a55f0e73b315d17b5691d7d">DD</a>-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfdebug/#ab7782075e0f7e6801bd76aadc2f753a0">useDWARF2Bitfields</a>()) &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01729" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1729"><Highlight kind="normal">        uint64&#95;t HiMark = (<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a05f5b9a11bdcc5feba62899f95dcf878a3134224cba2545bc57954d3b072aebb4">Offset</a> + FieldSize) &amp; AlignMask;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01730" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1730"><Highlight kind="normal">        uint64&#95;t FieldOffset = (HiMark - FieldSize);</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01731" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1731"><Highlight kind="normal">        <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a05f5b9a11bdcc5feba62899f95dcf878a3134224cba2545bc57954d3b072aebb4">Offset</a> -= FieldOffset;</Highlight></CodeLine>
